description: Fresh off his starring role in the Dialogues Lecture at the Society for Neuroscience conference in San Diego, jazz legend Pat Metheny discusses music and the brain, his creative process, and what was not covered during the lecture. He is also talks about his evolution as a musician, his mentors, and his views on commercial success and aging.
